Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveOyo Deputy Governor Rauf Olaniyan has defected from the PDP to the All Progressives Congress (APC).
Olaniyan announced his defection f in a chat with reporters on Sunday.
He and his principal Gov. Seyi Makinde have been at war for a while.
He governor has picked one of his appointees as his running mate in the coming guber election.
The defection puts to rest insinuations on his estranged relationship with Governor Seyi Makinde.
